Portfolio-Level Final Insight (to place below the table)

Across markets, CCAML volumes are concentrated in a few countries, standalone credit card exposure remains limited, and correlation with MANTAS AML events is generally low. Higher correlation percentages in certain low-volume markets are driven by scale rather than increased risk relevance. Overall, the majority of CCAML cases continue to be investigated independently, with risk-relevant outcomes observed across both correlated and non-correlated cases.

